==Useful Info==
'''Rats''' are one of the earliest and least powerful opponents in the game. They have average speed and are almost harmless, though some of their [[list of rats|later relatives]] are much more aggressive. They are most common in early levels of [[the Dungeon]] and in [[the Sewers]].

==Tips & Tricks==
*You can summon your own rats through use of the [[Summon Small Mammal]] spell.
*Although they are weak, rats place surprisingly high on the [http://crawl.akrasiac.org/scoring/killers.html list] of top killers. Don't let them nibble on you while you fight other monsters!

==History==
*Prior to [[0.31]], rats did not [[shout|squeak]].
